  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px; color: rgb(163, 163, 163) !important;\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" class=\"js_darkmode__0\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(34, 34, 34);font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(163, 163, 163) !important;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-shadow:transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27.2px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <div mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n    <div mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n     <div data-id=\"85660\" data-custom=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" data-color=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: currentcolor; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__3\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: currentcolor;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n      <div data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 2em; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-right-style: none; border-left-style: none; text-decoration: inherit; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em 0px 0px;padding: 0.5em 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);border-top: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;border-right-style: none;border-left-style: none;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n       <p mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"29.75\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: -1.2em; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; text-align: center; font-family: inherit; border-width: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: currentcolor; visibility: visible; line-height: 29.75px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__5\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;text-align: center;font-family: inherit;border-width: initial;border-style: initial;border-color: currentcolor;visibility: visible;line-height: 29.75px;\"><span mp-original-font-size=\"15\" mp-original-line-height=\"29.75\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:15px;line-height:29.75px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;background-color:rgb(117, 117, 118);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">机器之心报道</span></span></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">机器之心编辑部</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">AI 时代，智能体对短期对话的处理能力已不再是难题。真正的挑战是让智能体在数百步的探索中依然保持清晰的推理与稳健的决策。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">传统的强化学习框架在几十步内尚能应付，但一旦任务延展至数百步，奖励稀疏、历史冗长、策略崩塌便接踵而至。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了应对这些挑战，来自卡内基梅隆大学、香港大学等机构的研究者提出了 Verlog ，试图打破这一困境。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">具体而言，Verlog 是一个多轮强化学习框架，专为具有高度可变回合（episode）长度的长时程（long-horizon） LLM-Agent 任务而设计。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">它在继承 VeRL 和 BALROG 的基础上，并遵循 pytorch-a2c-ppo-acktr-gail 的成熟设计原则，引入了一系列专门优化手段，从而在任务跨度从短暂交互到数百回合时，依然能够实现稳定而高效的训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">以往的框架（如 VeRL 和 RAGEN）能够较好地处理约 10 回合的任务，verl-agent 则可扩展至 50 回合。而 Verlog 则被设计用于超过 400 回合的环境，使其在复杂的长期决策任务中具备独特优势。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这一能力已在 BabyAI、BabaIsAI 和 Crafter 等高难度领域得到验证。以 Crafter 为例，其回合长度范围在 70 到 400 步之间，平均约为 190 步。在这些充满挑战的环境中，Verlog 都能够开箱即用地展现出强劲的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503508537\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3153409090909091\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1056\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1056\" data-height=\"333\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"182\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=65d56914&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8Ux4ORDwpGNqaoDqFGNe3ayXgtj1GejotzxslUn3g1vlE2QEbIh16DbmVibBMyc8xt1e3v3cNVWDA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">博客地址：<a href=\"https://blog.ml.cmu.edu/2025/09/15/verlog-a-multi-turn-rl-framework-for-llm-agents/\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.ml.cmu.edu/2025/09/15/verlog-a-multi-turn-rl-framework-for-llm-agents/</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">项目主页：<a href=\"https://agentic-intelligence-lab.org/2025/08/15/technical-post.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://agentic-intelligence-lab.org/2025/08/15/technical-post.html</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"513\" data-backw=\"578\" data-height=\"625\" data-imgfileid=\"503508547\" data-ratio=\"0.8877840909090909\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"704\" data-width=\"704\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eda5ab63&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8Ux4ORDwpGNqaoDqFGNe3aqPHhSvBFMbl0Q9UGicFX8WyhyBWg8iceOC4YEclQzIDCWEPoibMElfVaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">方法介绍</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">基础模型</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在模型方面，本文基于 Qwen-2.5 的 Instruct 变体（Qwen-2.5-3B/7B-Instruct）构建。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这样做主要有两个原因：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一是，它可以与 BALROG 无缝集成（BALROG 是一个旨在评估 Instruct 模型在一系列基准测试中零样本性能的框架）；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">其次，它允许研究者可以直接使用基准测试提示，而无需太多修改。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503508549\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3076923076923077\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1014\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1014\" data-height=\"312\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"178\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3e3a8a91&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8Ux4ORDwpGNqaoDqFGNe3aanfEpic3sehYvW7K9YtGoPzmk9jbd2GbIWAW0Xh1WiaFJlM0DyahYOWQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">BabyAI 使用的提示模板</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">记忆机制</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">本文不是将整个轨迹全部放入上下文窗口中，而是仅保留最新的 n + 1 个回合。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这样做带来的影响是，对于 3B 参数的 Qwen 模型，性能在 n = 1 或 2 时达到峰值，而当 n 增加到 4 或 8 时性能下降。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">作者推测，模型性能下降的原因是 3B 模型在处理长上下文方面的能力有限，例如，当 n = 8 时，提示词长度约为 4600 个 token。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不过，这一趋势是否适用于更大规模的模型，仍待研究。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Dual Discounting GAE 算法</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了鼓励智能体在更少的环境步数内完成任务，本文将 token&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503508550\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2711864406779661\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"177\" style=\"width:97px;height:26px;\" data-width=\"177\" data-height=\"48\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b04652bf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8Ux4ORDwpGNqaoDqFGNe3a9Nibh26LPF77yBvxuYyN1fbSkbltBknJC9OQEIIeFVL0yvfE8bdeBEQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">与 step&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503508551\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.26174496644295303\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"149\" style=\"width:85px;height:22px;\" data-width=\"149\" data-height=\"39\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2fc61485&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8Ux4ORDwpGNqaoDqFGNe3atfsIU0ibqn6EAF8bCibQqQAy8U9ibBpbDKPtSL2hKZaDnyRrHlwRMBmBQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">进行了解耦。并设置如下参数：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503508552\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24358974358974358\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"390\" data-width=\"390\" data-height=\"95\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b56ad430&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8Ux4ORDwpGNqaoDqFGNe3aNLeZNVPWEhNaHUciaH9Re3fYHquISr60VB963XXQNXNt5RKb2u4NSKA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此外，本文 GAE 是递归计算的：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503508553\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.184\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"375\" data-width=\"375\" data-height=\"69\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=987410c3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8Ux4ORDwpGNqaoDqFGNe3aQfg9ICnlG0WO8B0iaVmUMPcIQEmDL0yu8PZnmhhnRWPGt1vHS8v2RicA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">其中，</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503508554\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2132701421800948\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"633\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 123px;\" data-width=\"633\" data-height=\"135\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=63f8ae81&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8Ux4ORDwpGNqaoDqFGNe3aibgtEw9elL2WUEMRB3rjWAabibxYEaZtFGmwpvaAEfrncwn6p245TIuw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">递归从最后一轮的最后一个 token 开始，向后进行。处理完最后一轮的所有 token 后，移至倒数第二轮的最后一个 token，并继续递归执行此过程。在此过程中，所有状态 token 都会被跳过。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503508555\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.41241890639481\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"232\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=43f023b4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FKmXPKA19gW8Ux4ORDwpGNqaoDqFGNe3a24Wx4PXn19icps2P2RMJSichJ9SGDVmXCz2uQMdg07l5vQnLsRI7oChw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">实验结果</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">该研究在三个颇具挑战性的基准上测试了 Verlog：包括 Crafter、BabyAI 和 BabaIsAI。实验模型包括 Qwen2.5-Instruct 。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503508561\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.91625\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"800\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"530\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ef1bee5e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FKmXPKA19gW8Ux4ORDwpGNqaoDqFGNe3aQLNM9cnJH1OMlPc6Kar0xQcTia3dOFv0mzicibzC3kGTJcG1ACe6YFPHA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 Crafter 环境中，本文使用 8 张 H100（82GB 显存）GPU 对 Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct 模型训练了大约 36 小时。此外，针对 BabyAI 与 BabaIsAI 环境，本文采用 4 张 A40（48GB 显存）GPU 对 Qwen2.5-3B-Instruct 模型训练约 24 小时。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">三个实验环境表明，Verlog 展现出稳定的训练能力，不管是在长周期、稀疏奖励，还是在可变 episode 长度条件下。这也证明了该框架能自然适应从短周期到超长周期多回合任务的规模化训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">总结</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Verlog 针对在构建长时程、多回合任务的 LLM Agent 时面临的若干核心工程挑战，提出了系统性的解决方案，包括：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">长交互历史的处理：通过记忆机制和回合级抽象来管理历史信息。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">稀疏奖励下的训练稳定性：结合 dual-discounting GAE 和价值函数预训练来增强稳定性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">轨迹长度可变的管理：通过固定回合批处理（fixed-turn batching）和自举式价值估计来处理变长轨迹。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">提升动作有效性：利用针对性的提示工程和默认动作替换，使训练过程中 &gt;95% 的动作均为有效动作。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">作者表示，Verlog 的定位是一个灵活的研究平台，目的是推动长时程 LLM-Agent 强化学习的发展。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Verlog 是一个开源多轮强化学习框架，专为解决 LLM 智能体在数百回合长时程任务中推理与决策稳定性挑战而设计。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Verlog 是一个开源多轮强化学习框架，专为解决 LLM 智能体在数百回合长时程任务中推理与决策稳定性挑战而设计。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了 Verlog，一个**开源**的、专为长时程（long-horizon）LLM 智能体任务设计的多轮强化学习框架。传统强化学习框架在处理数十步任务时表现尚可，但面对数百步的长时程任务时，常遭遇奖励稀疏、历史冗长和策略崩塌等问题。为应对这些挑战，来自卡内基梅隆大学和香港大学等机构的研究者提出了 Verlog。该框架在继承 VeRL 和 BALROG 的基础上，并遵循 pytorch-a2c-ppo-acktr-gail 的设计原则，引入了一系列专门优化手段，包括创新的记忆机制、Dual Discounting GAE 算法以及针对性的提示工程，使其能够稳定高效地处理长达 400 回合的复杂任务。Verlog 已在 BabyAI、BabaIsAI 和 Crafter 等高难度环境中验证了其卓越性能，旨在成为推动长时程 LLM 智能体强化学习发展的灵活研究平台。",
